    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not-assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 at MRL 2. Hemolysis index prediction error of 9.8% satisfies the 15% acceptance criterion. The model is judged fit for the purpose of identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device described in the Claim and Requirement documentation. Decision: Accepted.",
